        {
          "anchor" : "Overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This library defines the Uniform Type Identifier ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Automerge\/UniformTypeIdentifiers\/UTType\/automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : "  for the bytes that make up an Automerge document.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This type is used in the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/com.github.automerge.automerge-swift\/documentation\/Automerge\/Document\/transferRepresentation",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " property of an Automerge document, to conform Automerge documents to the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/coretransferable\/transferable",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Defining-a-type-for-your-file-format",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Defining a type for your file format",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The identifier for the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " type is ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "com.github.automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", and the provided type conforms to the type ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "public.data",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "When defining a type for your app, as described in ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/uniformtypeidentifiers\/defining_file_and_data_types_for_your_app",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", you may conform your own app’s type to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Automerge\/UniformTypeIdentifiers\/UTType\/automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " if you are using the bytes from ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/com.github.automerge.automerge-swift\/documentation\/Automerge\/Document\/save()",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " as the on-disk representation.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "If your file format wraps those bytes, then provide your own type definition that does not conform to the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " type.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you use the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "automerge",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " type directly, define the type as an imported type within the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Info.plist",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " file for your app.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "The details are most easily updated in the Imported Type Definitions panel of the Info panel for your app’s target in Xcode.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "definition" : {
                "content" : [
                  {
                    "inlineContent" : [
                      {
                        "code" : "Automerge document",
